    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_27_400-436",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "400-436",
      "markText": "日本人不拿台湾人当日本人，而大陆人却以为台湾人是日本人，台湾人究竟是谁？",
      "totalCount": 1326,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=400&rangeEnd=436",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=400&rangeEnd=436"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_13_1114-1210",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1114-1210",
      "markText": "郑氏孤忠，得遗民人心，不是为了朱家天下，而是为了维护华夏文化的一脉香火，所以郑氏和清政府屡次谈判，可以称臣，但是坚持不剃发，不改衣冠，只是为了保留华夏文化的象征。这一立场，乃是为了文化的归属。",
      "totalCount": 1078,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1114&rangeEnd=1210",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1114&rangeEnd=1210"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_28_1524-1597",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1524-1597",
      "markText": "这样的文化土壤，不会十分丰厚。再加上族群之间的分类斗争长期存在，分类的认同和归属感又是基于现实利益，往往超越了，也分散了文化的归属感和民族的认同。",
      "totalCount": 954,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1524&rangeEnd=1597",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1524&rangeEnd=1597"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_48_623-674",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "623-674",
      "markText": "我的愿望是：璧合之前须有珠联，镜圆之后还待金镶，其间必有一个过程，一个秉承善意和理性、彼此相处的过程。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=623&rangeEnd=674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=623&rangeEnd=674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_69_638-677",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "638-677",
      "markText": "台湾需要忧患意识，只有想到将来会发生不敢想象的后果，才会鼓起勇气，努力找出路。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=638&rangeEnd=677",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=69&rangeStart=638&rangeEnd=677"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_36_696-788",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "696-788",
      "markText": "日本人不拿台湾人当日本人，而大陆人却以为台湾人是日本人，台湾人究竟是谁？在作家吴浊流笔下，台湾人是亚细亚的孤儿。这种尴尬的局面，反映在台湾今天的文化归属和认同上，依旧是一个很大的问号。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=696&rangeEnd=788",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=696&rangeEnd=788"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300116201_38_1373-1466",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "1373-1466",
      "markText": "当时全岛准备欢迎中华民国的国军，但是从码头上下来的，却是衣衫褴褛、装备粗劣、训练不足的一群军人。在台湾同胞的印象中，日本军队训练有素、装备精良，两者相比，对中国军队的形象，陡然大失所望。",
      "totalCount": 738,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300116201&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1373&rangeEnd=1466",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cf8329c0813ab93e4g011ade?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1373&rangeEnd=1466"
    },
    {
